data.description: Huge price drop on this unique and Serene 4 bedroom 2.5 full bathrooms home sits on a breathtaking 40 acres! Great location less than 2 miles from the entrance to Joshua Tree National Park and Tortoise Rock Casino. Enjoy the spectacular panoramic mountain views from the front of this home, amazing views out of every window, as well as the entire valley city light views from the back of the home.   This home has large custom floor tiles, wall to wall carpet, Formal living room, Formal Dining room, upgraded kitchen with custom tiled island, as well as a family room with hand crafted gas or wood burning fireplace built with rocks. The former owners gathered on the 40 acres this home sits on for recreational fun. Mule Deer has been spotted enjoying this acreage as well.  Master bedroom suite includes a cozy electric burning fireplace as well as a large patio door leading to the enormous covered back patio. The Master Bathroom has a custom Jacuzzi tub with separate glass shower stall, and dual sinks. An enormous covered back patio complete with recessed lighting, desert scape views that allows plenty of room to entertain. This unique home sitting on 40 acres giving your family room  to roam. This massive and beautiful acreage is great for horses, animals, and all your R.V.'s! Must see to appreciate.  Video available on request
